      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "According to the template, the number of pads and power pads is fixed and cannot be changed. I assume this is to comply with the default floorplan and the PCB wire-bonding scheme.\n\nSo, even if we do not actually use that many IO cells, we still need to place that many IO cells, is that correct?",
