      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "If you want more pins than are on the default padring you are more on your own. \n\n@ReJ aka Renaldas Zioma is making a design that has fewer needed pads, but is leaving the others present like in his drawing here https://discord.com/channels/1361349522684510449/1408134567491145728/1442207041593806851\n\nBut changing the number I believe would change the positions, which would not make it compatible with our current standards. \nLike @Tim 'mithro' Ansell said, others may be able to speak more confidently about what changes are really possible",
      "author": {
